##### Company

Lytics, the pioneer of adaptive digital marketing, provides marketers with a marketing activation platform that integrates all touch points, surfaces previously undiscoverable behaviors of customers and prospects, then proactively recommends how to best target audiences across web, mobile, email and social.


##### Integration


Connect Lytics with Optimizely to deliver personalized, 1:1 experiences to site visitors that improve test results, conversion rates and drive revenue growth.

With Lytics & Optimizely, integrate customer data across email, social, websites and mobile to surface previously undiscoverable audiences.   Using that data, Lytics SmartAudience™ segments and suggests opportunities to create targeted, personalized experiences based on audience behavior across all marketing channels. Pass Lytics SmartAudience™ to Optimizely using the native Optimizely CustomTags code.
